Array: Ladies and gentlemen, prepare to be astounded, for there is a new troupe in town!
Their renown has increased, so please, dear audience, let your applause rise like thunder and lift their spirits high!
And now, behold, as the whimsicality of artistic inspiration quickens amongst them!
The curtain falls for now, but fret not, we shall meet again under the grand lights of the ring!
Maximum renown? Why, bravo, my marvelous stars!
You have dazzled, you have soared, and you have left your mark upon the world!
But every grand performance must come to a close. While the wonder will never fade, it is time for the lights to dim.
Let's hear it one last time for the one, the only....
